Variable is a container which can hold data
to represent data we need variables

int x = 100
int age = 25
float price = 150.41
double price = 150.41
String name = "Steven"
char sex = 'F'


Data types
---------------------------
Data type represents type of data 

1. Primitive data types

byte, short, int, long --> number without decimal
float, double ---> decimal number
char ----> single character (single quote)
boolean ---> true/false


2. Non-Primitive data types / Derived / Collections
String
ArrayList
HashMap
HashSet
etc... 


















